# sample json for a small Ceph cluster
# all values are strings unless otherwise stated
# top-level dictionary contains:
#   region - optional, default us-east
#   image -  optional, default linode/centos7
#   roles -  required, list of ceph-ansible roles  
#   for each role:
#       count - integer, number of linodes in role
#       prefix - which ansible role, also used to generate label
#       plan - unique substring of a linode plan id
#       osd-size-GB - optional, integer, default 20 (GB)
#       osds-per-host - optional, integer default 1
